    @startuml C2_Manage_Vessel_Types_Process_View
    title C2 – Manage Vessel Types (Process View – Create Vessel Type)

    actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
    participant "Frontend Web Application\n(React / Angular)" as Frontend
    participant "Vessel Types Management API\n(ASP.NET Core Web API)" as API
    participant "External IAM Provider\n(SSO / OAuth 2.0)" as IAM
    database "PLMS Database\n(SQL / EF Core)" as DB


    Officer -> Frontend : Login (Credenciais)
    Frontend -> IAM : Solicita token de autenticação
    IAM --> Frontend : Retorna Access Token (JWT)


    Officer -> Frontend : Submete formulário (novo tipo de navio)
    Frontend -> API : POST /api/VesselTypes (JSON + Token JWT)
    API -> IAM : Valida Token (OAuth 2.0)
    IAM --> API : Token válido


    API -> DB : INSERT INTO VesselTypes (...)
    DB --> API : Confirma inserção (OK)


    API --> Frontend : HTTP 201 Created + VesselTypeDTO
    Frontend --> Officer : Mostra confirmação e novo tipo de navio

    @enduml
